reviews.text:
Mala atencion, fui a comprar bicarbonato de sodio y además de la malla atención la bolsa de bicarbonato decía 9kn (9 kunas), me cobro 15 y no quizo explicarme porque cobraba de mas, como la necesitaba tuve que pagar el sobreprecio. Se que es una experiencia personal, pero esta situacion de sobreprecio puede vivirla otro.

Vayan a la otra que esta a 30 metros sobre la otra mano de la stardus.
Très belle pharmacie avec son cloître juste à côté
Profesionalno i uredno ko svaka ljekarna 💊
Fantastic place, super friendly staff and lovely quality rooms with ample off street parking. Highly recommend and will be back next visit.....  😁

Have stayed at The View a few times now. Reception staff are always amazing and deserve five stars alone!

Rooms are cosy but not in a bad way, they are kept very clean and have everything you need (bar a microwave). Bed and pillows are comfy and feel clean. Bathroom/Shower is clean also. Has Foxtel.

Food from the restaurant is pretty good if you can make the cut off times. Prices are up there a little though.

Possibly the only issue I have is security around the parking area. Although plenty of spaces to go around, if/when we park in the back street there’s so many shady characters who  lurk and try sneak a peek in everyone’s car when pretending to walk past regardless of the couple of cameras there.. They don’t care..

I guess there’s not exactly any other option except for extra cctv cameras and lighting hence I’m still happy to give five stars.

Pretty annoyed to be arriving at 6.30 pm to be told there is no food service. As an older woman traveling alone  and no vehicle I’m really not about to go heading off in the dark looking for somewhere to eat. I booked directly with the motel site too so I should have been informed, and that was only a few weeks ago, you should have had the courtesy to let me know so I could make arrangements. Very badly managed.
Clean quiet rooms close to the shops.
Very clean new room. Wifi is fast as there must be a modem in every room, my room has one anyway. Room service is great. Nice food. I haven't finished my stay yet as I am already impressed. 👌🏼
